{
  "stem": "7938.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, once in Plaszow, we had to look-- we had to do something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Otherwise, we would have gone to any menial work every morning, to knocking stones or whatever there is.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was dangerous not to do anything, because as the picture of Goth shows, if he saw somebody not doing anything, he was shooting from his balcony.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was aiming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I worked in the-- in the-- in the bath house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the bath house, whatever they needed there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They need to move something, they need to bring to-- to-- to repair some faucets, or whatever there is.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They needed somebody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a big chimney near the bath house, and there was-- there was a stair-- a staircase, which [INAUDIBLE] you could go on the top.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I tried-- I tried not to be in the limelight so that nobody can see me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even one day, Himmler came in for a-- for looking over the camp, because this was, for him, a new camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- at that time, I didn't want to be even on the main floor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I went up on the chimney, and I stayed-- I stayed there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, I started making-- I started looking for some job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And since they told me about Emalia, I asked and I received an assignment to Emalia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I also-- I also started later for my wife and for my sister, for all my family so that finally, when it came to the end, we all-- we were all at Emalia and we went together to Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Including my brother-in-law, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My wife's mother died in the ghetto before-- before the-- before the liquidation of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
